description: Imagine the Possibilities! Excellent  opportunity to own a single-family, fully detached  home with an attached one car garage on a desirable street! Work with your contractor and design plans to renovate the home to your liking, creating a space that truly reflects your style and needs. Enjoy  peekaboo views of Lake Merced from the living room. Good sized backyard offers privacy and extra space, great for relaxation, entertaining, personal enjoyment.  Property records indicate that the property is a 1bedroom, 1bath home, however, the additional room at the back of the home provides potential for customization and could be utilized in various ways depending on your needs such as another bedroom or home office. Virtual images are for entertainment purposes only and do not reflect actual size or property dimensions. The property is a fixer upper. Buyer to fully investigate all aspects of the property such as current condition, interior square footage & lot size prior to making an offer.
